summary: A replacement of Anise\'s Cabin located South West of Riverwood. A fully functional Player home with many unique features, simple but including the necessities for game play. Standalone and relatively lore-friendly.
descriptionHtml:
A replacement of Anise\'s Cabin located South West of Riverwood. A fully functional Player home with many unique features, simple but including the necessities for game play. Standalone and relatively lore-friendly.

Features Simple Unique Storage
(In game appearance followed by storage use or purpose)

 . deer pelt, pelts and hides
 . leather strip, leathers
 . silver ingot, ingots
 . ore bucket, ores
 . unique weapons rack
 . weapons rack
 . staff rack
 . bows and arrows rack
 . heavy armor cupboard
 . light armor cupboard
 . potions wall shelf
 . poisons wall shelf
 . unique stones of Barenziah soul gem case
 . ingredients drawer
 . mead, ale, wine shelf
 . fruits and vegetables basket

Other Notable Features

 . tiny garden
 . 3 full weapon/ shield plaques
 . 2 shield plaques
 . 6 dagger display cases
 . player owned bed
 . night table (vanilla storage)
 . enchanting table
 . alchemy table
 . cooking spit and pot
 . full smithing station including smelter
 . 2 bookshelves hold 14 books each

Added Unique Scripted Features

 . Initial sweep of the shack to clear the scattered hay from the floors
 . Interactive combat dummy which will advance the player\'s level
 . \"Tune\" the lute to play a melody (A, B, C, or D)

Please report any bugs in the comments section of this mod\'s nexus page (HERE)
author: HaileySkyrim
